{"id":14144,"date":"2025-10-24T11:53:46","date_gmt":"2025-10-24T15:53:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=evenement&#038;p=14144"},"modified":"2025-11-03T14:11:28","modified_gmt":"2025-11-03T19:11:28","slug":"soiree-bingo-au-profit-des-orm","status":"publish","type":"evenement","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/evenement\/soiree-bingo-au-profit-des-orm\/","title":{"rendered":"Soir\u00e9e Bingo au profit des ORM"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Cette ann\u00e9e, afin de donner un coup de pouce aux diff\u00e9rents projets \u00e9tudiants, la <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/vie-etudiante\/\">Vie \u00e9tudiante<\/a> propose une soir\u00e9e bingo !<\/p>\n<p>Chaque dollar r\u00e9colt\u00e9 \u00e0 la suite de la vente de cartes de bingo ira directement aux projets \u00e9tudiants. Plusieurs prix seront \u00e0 gagner durant la soir\u00e9e.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Comment participer<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Passez chercher vos coupons au F103.<\/p>\n<p>Un coupon se vend 20\u00a0$ et comprend trois\u00a0cartes de bingo, une pour chaque jeu, une pointe de pizza ou un hot dog et un paquet de croustilles.<\/p>\n<p>Vente de cartes \u00e0 l\u2019unit\u00e9 pour 5\u00a0$ au profit de votre projet, vente de boissons alcoolis\u00e9es ou non et de nourriture.<\/p>\n<p><strong>D\u00e9roulement de la soir\u00e9e<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>16\u00a0h\u00a030 \u00e0 18\u00a0h\u00a030\u00a0: accueil festif<br \/>\n18\u00a0h\u00a045 \u00e0 19\u00a0h\u00a020\u00a0: premi\u00e8re carte<br \/>\n19\u00a0h\u00a030 \u00e0 20\u00a0h\u00a05\u00a0: deuxi\u00e8me carte<br \/>\n20\u00a0h\u00a015 \u00e0 21\u00a0h\u00a0: troisi\u00e8me carte<\/p>\n<p>De nombreux prix, un DJ et bien plus vous attend \u00e0 cette soir\u00e9e pleine de rebondissements\u2009!<\/p>\n<p>\u00c0 vos cartes, pr\u00eats, party\u2009!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":14146,"template":"","categorieevenement":[193],"etiquette-interne":[2287,2357],"class_list":["post-14144","evenement","type-evenement","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorieevenement-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-milieu-de-vie"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:37:25","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"categorieevenement"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/evenement\/14144","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/evenement"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/evenement"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/14146"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14144"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"categorieevenement","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categorieevenement?post=14144"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=14144"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}